10 OVERSTAY PATIENT BY COORDINATING BETWEEN HOSPITALS, RELEVANT STATE
11 AGENCIES AND PROGRAMS, AND PROVIDERS OF MENTAL HEALTH AND SUBSTANCE
12 USE DISORDER SERVICES.
