23 4. one representative of Maryland Legal Aid;
24 5. one representative of the Court Appointed Special
25 Advocates of Maryland;
26 6. one representative of the National Association of Social
27 Workers – Maryland who is a hospital–based clinical social worker;
28 7. one representative of the Maryland Chapter of the
29 American Academy of Pediatrics;
